    <content type='html'>Xetoil, thank you very much for your comments!
I have amended Odessa&amp;#39;s physical description and a few other details.  Please let me know what you think!

For comparison&amp;#39;s sake, here is the original description:

She wore soft, flat-soled boots, cargo pants with a simple leather belt, a fitted T-shirt, and a lightweight long-sleeved top with the sleeves usually rolled up.  She carried her belongings in a spacious backpack, with lots of pockets and compartments.  Her long tight black curls cascaded over her shoulders and bobbled energetically when she moved.  Her eyes were the colour of dark oak and were set underneath a pair of bold black eyebrows; she had a habit of scanning every detail.  When she focused her attention on you, you could almost feel the information being syphoned.  When she daydreamed, which she did often, she tended to tilt her head to one side and look up out of the corner of her left eye with slightly parted lips.  And when someone she especially loved held her close, she liked to purr softly, sometimes with a French R, sometimes trilled, and brush his cheek with hers.</content>
